ate complex concepts into easily understood termsDemonstrated ability to develop and deliver effective and engaging library instructionStrong project management and organizational skillsDemonstrated initiative, creativity, and problem-solving skillsProven event planning and social media content creation skillsAcademic credentials or work experience in the creative arts an asset Compensation $45.88 - $94.99 Closes: 12 January, 2025 Langara College Vancouver , BC Policies and Terms of Use · jobboard@bcla.bc.ca / BCLA PO BOX 19008, Rocky Point PO, Port Moody, BC V3H 0J1 window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
